#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "kqml User's Manual"
msgstr "kqml उपयोगकर्ता पुस्तिका"

#. Tag: date
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "2023-06-10"
msgstr "२०२३-०६-१०"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma 6.0"
msgstr "प्लाज्मा ६.०"

#. Tag: productname
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "KDE Plasma"
msgstr "केडीई प्लाज्मा"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<मन्वोल्नुम्>१</मन्वोल्नुम्>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "QML Runtime with KLocalizedContext"
msgstr "KLocalizedContext इत्यनेन सह QML Runtime"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kqml</command> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-v, --version</"
"option></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-h, --help</option></group> "
"<group choice=\"opt\"><option>-d, --domain</option> <replaceable>domain</"
"replaceable></group> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>files</replaceable>..."
"</arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><option>--</option> <replaceable>args</"
"replaceable>...</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kqml</command><group choice=\"opt\"><option value=\"-v, --version"
"\"> -व, --संस्करणम्</option></group><group choice=\"opt\"><option value=\"-h, --"
"help\"> -ह, --सहाय</option></group><group choice=\"opt\"><option value=\"-d, "
"--domain\"> -d, --domain इति</option><replaceable> क्षेत्र</replaceable></"
"group><arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable> सञ्चिकाः</replaceable> ...</arg><arg "
"choice=\"opt\"><option value=--> -- ९.</option><replaceable> अर्ग्स्</"
"replaceable> ...</arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kqml</command> is a QML runtime with initialized KLocalizedContext."
msgstr ""
"<command>kqml</command> इति प्रारम्भित KLocalizedContext इत्यनेन सह QML रनटाइम् "
"अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlike the qml tool that comes with qt-declarative package, kqml initializes "
"KLocalizedContext that allows testing real-world applications and scratch "
"files with i18n calls throughout their code and imported libraries."
msgstr ""
"qt-declarative संकुलेन सह आगच्छति qml साधनस्य विपरीतम्, kqml KLocalizedContext "
"इत्यस्य आरम्भं करोति यत् वास्तविक-दुनिया-अनुप्रयोगानाम् परीक्षणं कर्तुं शक्नोति तथा च i18n-"
"आह्वानैः सह स्क्रैच-सञ्चिकाः तेषां सम्पूर्णे कोड्-मध्ये आयातित-पुस्तकालयेषु च अनुमन्यते"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-v</option>, <option>--version</option>"
msgstr ""
"<option value=-v>-वि</option> , ९.<option value=--version> --संस्करण</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays version information."
msgstr "संस्करणसूचनाः प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-d</option>, <option>--domain</option> <replaceable>domain</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option value=-d>-घ</option> , ९.<option value=--domain> --क्षेत्र</"
"option><replaceable> क्षेत्र</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main localization domain."
msgstr "मुख्यं स्थानीयकरणक्षेत्रम् ।"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-h</option>, <option>--help</option>"
msgstr ""
"<option value=-h>-ह</option> , ९.<option value=--help> --साहाय्यम्‌</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays this help."
msgstr "एतत् साहाय्यं प्रदर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>files</replaceable>..."
msgstr "<replaceable>सञ्चिकाः</replaceable>..."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Any number of QML files can be loaded. They will share the same engine."
msgstr "यत्किमपि संख्यायां QML सञ्चिकाः लोड् कर्तुं शक्यन्ते । ते समानं इञ्जिनं साझां करिष्यन्ति।"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>args</replaceable>..."
msgstr "<प्रतिस्थापनीय>अर्ग्स्</प्रतिस्थापनीय>..."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arguments after '<option>--</option>' are ignored, but passed through to the "
"application.arguments variable in QML."
msgstr ""
"&#39; .&#39; परं तर्काः ।<option value=--> -- ९.</option> &#39; इत्यस्य अवहेलना "
"भवति, परन्तु QML मध्ये application.arguments चरपर्यन्तं पारितं भवति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "इदमपि पश्यन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More detailed user documentation is available from <ulink url=\"help:/plasma-"
"desktop\">help:/plasma-desktop</ulink> (either enter this <acronym>URL</"
"acronym> into &konqueror;, or run <userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> "
"<parameter>help:/plasma-desktop</parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"अधिकविस्तृतं उपयोक्तृदस्तावेजं <ulink url=\"help:/plasma-desktop\">help:/plasma-"
"desktop</ulink> इत्यस्मात् उपलभ्यते (एतत् <acronym>URL</acronym> इत्येतत् &konqueror; "
"इत्यत्र प्रविशन्तु, अथवा <userinput चालयन्तु ><command>khelpcenter</command> "
"<parameter>सहाय्यम्:/प्लाज्मा-डेस्कटॉप</parameter></userinput>) इति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "लेखकाः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kqml.1.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kqml</command> was written by <personname><firstname>ivan</"
"firstname><surname>tkachenko</surname></personname> <email>me@raitjas.tk</"
"email>."
msgstr ""
"<command>kqml</command> इति <personname><firstname>ivan</"
"firstname><surname>tkachenko</surname></personname> <email>me@raitjas.tk</"
"email> इत्यनेन लिखितम् ।"
